# Portfolio-Analysis-Library (PAL)

## WORK IN PROGRESS (WIP)

## Usage:
```
pip install portfolio-analysis-library
```

in python:
```
import pal
import pandas as pd
porfolio = pal.Portfolio(pd.Series([0.5, 0.5, 0.5]), 12)
portfolio.analysed_risk
```

## Development
```bash
pip install -r .[dev]
```


